'''Ghalesard''' ('''Qalesard''') is a village in the [[Zagros mountains]]. Its elevation from sea level is 1800 meters. 
'''Ghalesard_e bälä''' is another village, at an elevation of 2100 meters, that people migrate there each summer.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://telegram.me/qalesard|title=اقامتگاه‌بومگردی ‌قلعه‌سرد|website=Telegram|access-date=2017-07-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.Qalesard.blogfa.com|title=Qalesard Ecotourism Residence|website=www.qalesard.blogfa.com|access-date=2017-07-05}}</ref>

