== In sport == The [[South Zone cricket team (Bangladesh)|South Zone cricket team]] in [[Bangladesh]] is a [[first-class cricket]] team that represents southern Bangladesh ([[Khulna Division|Khulna]] and [[Barisal Division|Barisal]]) in the [[Bangladesh Cricket League]].
